::Shadow Wing::
She was outside of the Maximal base working on the bridge.  She heard shots 
being fired and explosions.  She turned to the others working on the bridge.
"You guys hear that?  I'm going to see what's going on over there.  That 
disburbance seams awefully close to the base."
She transformed into her beast mode and flew off towards the noises.
